---
title: TradeGecko Developer Portal

primary_cards:
  - name:  Ecommerce Integration Guide
    blurb: Build a sales channel integration with TradeGecko. Sync orders and products from your online stores and marketplaces.
    url: /guides/sales.html
    background_color: "#5784f7"
    image:
      url: /images/eCommerce@2x.png
  - name: Fulfillment Service Integration Guide
    blurb: Integrate TradeGecko with a fulfilment service to streamline your 3PL management and shipping workflows.
    url: /guides/3pl.html
    background_color: "#5bb4f9"
    image:
      url: /images/3PL@2x.png
  - name: Warehouse Management Integration Guide
    blurb: Sync inventory levels between your Warehouse Management System and TradeGecko.
    url: /guides/warehouse.html
    background_color: "#80dce2"
    image:
      url: /images/Warehouse@2x.png

secondary_cards:
  - name: Comprehensive API Docs
    blurb: Build exactly what you need with our modern APIs and webhooks.
    url: /docs.html
    cta: Explore docs
  - name: Detailed Guides and Tutorials
    blurb: TradeGeckoâ€™s thorough use cases provide step-by-step instructions to build integrations quickly and easily.
    url: /docs.html#guides
    cta: Explore guides
  - name: Knowledge and Support
    blurb: Detailed articles and getting started modules covering all areas of the TradeGecko product.
    url: https://support.tradegecko.com
    cta: Learn more

search: true
home: true
---
<div class="index-page">
  <div class="row index-page__section cta-section">
    <div class="col-12">
        <%= partial "includes/home_cta" %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row index-page__section">
    <div class="card-list">
      <% current_page.data.primary_cards.each do |study| %>
        <div class="study-card" style="background-color: <%=study.background_color%> ">
          <div class="study-card__image-wrapper">
            <img src="<%=study.image.url%>" />
          </div>
          <div class="study-blurb">
            <h2><%=study.name%></h2>
            <p><%=study.blurb%></p>
            <a href="<%=study.url%>" class="btn btn-big btn-primary card__sticky-button" >
              Read More
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row index-page__section">
    <h1> Start building with TradeGecko API in minutes...</h1>
  </div>

  <div class="row">
    <div class="card-list">
      <% current_page.data.secondary_cards.each do |study| %>
        <div class="study-card secondary-card">
          <div class="study-blurb">
            <h2><%=study.name%></h2>
            <p><%=study.blurb%></p>
            <a href="<%= study.url %>" class="plain-link card__sticky-button" >
              <%= study.cta %> <i class="fa fa-angle-right"></i>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row index-page__section">
    <div class="col-md-1">
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-3 become-partner__image">
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-7 become-partner__details">
      <h1> Sign up for a partner account to get started</h1>
      <p>Discover how our Partner Program can help your clients build the business of their dreams and make you money in the process</p>
      <a href="https://partners.tradegecko.com/register" target="blank_" class="btn btn-big btn-primary" >
        Become a partner
      </a>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-1">
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
